        "TileImage": "$($repository d895f323-64b6-4e55-8c75-e84cd3a48a53).Image",
        "Description": "The client said he needed to be taken care of. No reason. He probably did something wrong. I recommend you go long for this one, but you don&apos;t have to. Oh yeah, and the client is a bad rock climber, so show him how it&apos;s done. And also, there is some kind of virus called Divoc-91, I think it&apos;s still live so a little warning on that. Try not to kill anyone (keyword: try). Killing this man is pretty easy. Cameras show he likes chilling at the garden so you can find him there. By the way I like men",
